Class RawSource

edu.wpi.first.cscore.raw.RawSource
All Implemented Interfaces:
AutoCloseable
public class RawSource
extends ImageSource
A source for user code to provide video frames as raw bytes.

This is a complex API, most cases should use CvSource.
